attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Beautiful 3 bed/ 2.5 bath single-family home well situated in the heart of S Boston with easy access to Seaport and Logan Airport! Originally a mixed use property with a residence above a retail space, it has since been thoughtfully transformed into a spacious home. The first level features a large bedroom area (that doubles as a media and exercise room for the current owners) with ensuite bath. Featuring charming exposed beams and a brick accent wall this room is a perfect home office, additional living space or third bedroom. On the second level, you'll find a cozy living room with built-ins, a formal dining room, office, and an eat in kitchen boasting the original fireplace. Off of the kitchen is an outdoor entertainer's dream deck. The third level offers two generously sized bedrooms, a sitting room with walk in closet for the master bedroom, and a full bathroom adorned with elegant marble finishes. The home also includes the convenience of one covered parking space.
